                                "type": "text",
                                "text": " on his new book \"The Magic of Code\" (which is now on my reading list). A good reminder (for those who need it, perhaps not so much people here) that computing is not just utilitarian.\n\nSince Sam is around here, some short feedback:\n"
                            }
